{
  "stem": "293.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's [NON ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON ENGLISH]. 69006.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, it's easier for me to say from memory right away the German because this was very important.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They never number us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was strange, too, because we-- we were not supposed to say there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we will stay, we were not supposed to be alive, you see?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they didn't have to give us the number.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The number people were getting in Auschwitz, in Gross-Rosen, in Mauthausen, and Dachau only when they were considered that they will last there for few months and do the slave labor, you see?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then, when we found out that we leaving Gross-Rosen, what was a death camp-- you understand what I mean-- we start to breathe now.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where we get-- send us?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Probably to Schindler, to Brunnlitz, because there's no sense to throw us from Gross-Rosen to another camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we knew we were going to Schindler.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And about 24 hours later or two days later-- I don't remember the amount of time what passed by-- we found ourselves over there in Schindler's camp with the food waiting for us, with a place.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We slept on the floor because we have to build our wooden bed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What we did it ourself, but we were with him, so we were not afraid anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he told us-- I don't-- we start to ask him where is-- he knows Mila.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He knows my family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He knows Itzhak Stern, Moszek Bejski, and all those people who work with him, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We always were close to him and ask him, Herr Direktor, where are the women?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
